  "prompt": "Which is the best 43 inches Smart LED TV in India?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, several brands offer high-quality 43-inch Smart LED TVs in India. The best choice often depends on your specific needs, such as budget, preferred features, and brand loyalty. Here are some popular options that generally receive good reviews:\n\n1. **LG 43LM5650PTA**:\n   - Resolution: Full HD (1920 x 1080)\n   - WebOS platform with access to popular streaming apps\n   - Good sound quality and viewing angles\n   - ThinQ AI for smart features\n\n2. **Samsung UA43TU7200AKXXL**:\n   - Resolution: 4K UHD (3840 x 2160)\n   - Crystal Display technology for enhanced colors\n   - Tizen OS with a user-friendly interface\n   - Multiple connectivity options including HDMI and USB\n\n3. **Sony Bravia KDL-43W800G**:\n   - Resolution: Full HD (1920 x 1080)\n   - Android TV OS with Google Assistant built-in\n   - Excellent picture quality with vivid colors\n   - Good audio performance\n\n4. **OnePlus Y Series 43Y1**:\n   - Resolution: Full HD (1920 x 1080)\n   - Built-in Chromecast and Android TV\n   - Good sound quality with Dolby Audio\n   - Affordable price point\n\n5. **TCL 43P615**:\n   - Resolution: 4K UHD (3840 x 2160)\n   - Android TV with Google Assistant\n   - Good overall performance at a competitive price\n   - Supports HDR for better contrast\n\nBefore making a purchase, consider checking customer reviews, warranty options, and after-sales service for each brand. Prices may vary, so it's also a good idea to compare them across different retailers and platforms. Additionally, new models may have been released after my last update, so make sure to check the latest offerings and reviews.",
